<p>See <a href="https://inedo.com/support/documentation/proget/installation/installation-guide" class="uri">https://inedo.com/support/documentation/proget/installation/installation-guide</a> for more details. There is a Linux installation guide for Docker containers, however we don&#39;t recommend it for production use - <a href="https://inedo.com/support/documentation/proget/installation/installation-guide/linux-docker" class="uri">https://inedo.com/support/documentation/proget/installation/installation-guide/linux-docker</a>.</p>
